WEBVTT

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:32.416
My father is a doctor,

00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:36.016
and so we had a great advantage
having him in charge,

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:38.200
and he did a beautiful job
taking care of her.

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:41.496
But I, too, wanted to do
everything I could to help,

00:04:41.520 --> 00:04:44.096
so I wanted to try everything.

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:45.320
We all did.

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:47.656
I researched alternative medicines,

00:04:47.680 --> 00:04:50.760
diets, juicing, acupuncture.

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:52.976
Finally, I asked her,

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:54.600
"Is this what you want me to do?"

00:04:55.280 --> 00:04:56.520
And she said, "No."

00:04:57.360 --> 00:05:00.480
She said, "Pace yourself.
I'm going to need you later."